nodes.text: During the Battle of Yuuzhan'tar at the end of the Yuuzhan Vong War in 29 ABY, Bacta Squad, a unit of Judder Page's Katarn Commandos, battled Yuuzhan Vong warriors near Shimrra's Citadel. When Captain Page reached the citadel with the rest of his commandos, one member of the team, a Human sergeant, approached him and asked for backup. Page sent ten commandos.
